      "text": [
        " «أَيْنَ صَاحِبُهَا مُرُوهُ فَلْيَسْتَعِدَّ غَداً لِلْخُصُومَةِ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.2490 - Al-Sakuni narrated with his chain of transmission that the Prophet (peace and blessings of Allah (swt) be upon him and his family) saw a camel tied up with its gear still on it.\nProphet (sw) said: \"Where is its owner? Tell him to prepare for a dispute tomorrow (on the Day of Judgment).\""
        ]
      }
